Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:36.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8}第5道菜\N在某个感冒的日子里…、和平常不同的瓦古娜利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢  小鸟游
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我现在忽然注意到一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店的女员工的身高和年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有奇怪程度  是成正比的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(0,500)}奇怪程度图解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子最小的前辈  虽然有些比较强势的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但基本上性格温和  很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是伊波小姐  看上去很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有着极度的男性恐惧症
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有男人在身边  她马上就会揍过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领班的轰小姐  懂得察言观色  为人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作上也很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  带刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最怪的是旁若无人  又很暴力  不工作就知道吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原不良少女的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是最怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可不想被你这个变态说成是“最怪”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  和其他人比起来  我最正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经理音尾人虽然不错  但缺乏威严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在寻找行踪不明的妻子  不在店里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤表情生硬  眼神很凶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却出乎意料的亲切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他喜欢那位领班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相马  很会说话  好像和谁都能相处地很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知为何  他什么都知道  出乎意料的腹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前这么说  真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游才是  前段时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都有好好工作  也没什么不擅长的事  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我是最正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信满满地一口咬定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长  那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是儿童套餐的赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了是儿童套餐的赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不点餐是拿不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好恶心  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个快去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  工作工作～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千代  拜托你做圣代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我很乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做草莓巧克力味的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  种岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  是不是长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的佐藤也很欢乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤今天也一点都不会腻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰积极地照顾店长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当察觉到她一心向着店长的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤就在这个时候拿种岛出气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世上也不停着循环着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  真是非常精彩的恶循环
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  因为我小就总是耍我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没耍你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是会长大的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你啊  要是长大了打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想变成巨人  踩扁我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:15.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(500,500)}大巨人白杨咚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘎～丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘎～丝～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多恶劣的家伙啊  大恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鸟游  快帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  前辈  我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前羞鸟游还帮过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是佐藤抓住你什么小辫子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现被欺负的前辈也好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我不靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找别人帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒气冲冲的前辈  好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小白杨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千代  我被佐藤欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负弱者是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪边是弱者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道平时有什么让你很心烦气燥的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WORKING…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤…自从上次问他是不是喜欢杏子姐开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉变得好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我知道是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相马  你知道些什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…虽然很犹豫一些话该不该说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过佐藤他是有喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是店长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是我搞错了  他才生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  他喜欢的人是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想这么说  但是佐藤不让我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  提示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想  为什么他总是要找种岛的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个反应是没弄明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  佐藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间问了你是不是喜欢杏子姐的事  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了别提那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤你是喜欢小白杨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要再说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  佐藤  撞到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  种岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你太小了我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  真是的  又耍人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭佐藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个负连锁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我都想问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐你真的有想过治好你的男人恐惧症吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有想过嘛  我也很努力了嘛  比之前也好多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可以让男人接近你到什么程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2…2米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之我能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被表扬了就会进步的人  哼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么收尾台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鸟游  为什么要和小伊吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…算是很平常的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一点也没进步  让人有点火大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小伊她一直有在努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鸟游…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  今天还只是第三拳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他渐渐习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明比我小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我才是前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我做得还不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真昼  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照店长所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去习惯小鸟游  习惯男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算小鸟游挂掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要搭上人命比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不太清楚  但别破坏墙壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧从早上开始就退不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好躺着了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  现在还在诊疗时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是去医院看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是哥哥  打工那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打电话请假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游要带他生病的妹妹去医院  说今天请假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…嗯  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真昼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说小鸟游今天请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  刚才在店长那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小伊  今天羞鸟游请假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  为什么都要对我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小伊  要是小鸟游不在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寂寞吗  不会想揍人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我又不是和主人分开的小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游要是不在也没什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全  没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？最近揍的好像都是小鸟游呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小鸟游请假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是不在的话  我被揍的几率就会上升的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  佐藤你都没被揍过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为我每天都想好相应措施了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对小伊害怕过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她确实是挺可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这想成是店里有个搞突然袭击的片花节目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我可没那么乐观…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是多试着接近一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了遇到的那一刻  在脑内演习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说呢…假设在整理仓库时  偶然与伊波相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  把人家弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在这种情况下说的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又打人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机也忘记放进柜子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是相马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  相…相马  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是  那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道我的手机号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  我以为你会马上挂电话的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还可以说上话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前这样还是行不通的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  是有在慢慢变好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这全都是伊波的饲主小鸟游的功劳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  墙坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是相马你说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.07,0:15:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…那个…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确我是受到了小鸟游不少照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是像狗一样依赖着他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  在电话那头我被揍扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  小伊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所看到的  打电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只看到你在店里搞破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点去前厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人马上要多起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰是早班  已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小鸟游也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要点的菜决定好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她基本上算是个好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小伊冰释前嫌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.30,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心灵上有点接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机真伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就一辈子都不用正面接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是接近了吗？还是更远了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人增加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为小鸟游不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前厅就会变得很忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  偏偏在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来的都是男性客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  两位客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11位客人吗  请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都是男人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  客人接连不断的来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是男性顾客  种岛一个人接待不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房的人能帮忙接客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  我讨厌接客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要拿出勇气加油哦  伊波
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个与其说是拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是威胁…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之已经叫了八千代了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙家离这里很远  要过来还要一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏…杏子姐  你可以去大厅帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是可以做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要后悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波负责记帐和甜点之类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做自己能做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长负责收银
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种岛加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候一定要多加把劲才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  嘿  哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤  挺适合你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天黑下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 医院很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打针以后似乎好多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过我还是不太喜欢打针
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去以后注意保暖 然后好好睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然请假 餐厅不会有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前对伊波会不会说得太过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏子姐去收银了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,种岛一个人在大厅忙不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤和相马也到大厅帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  佐藤  厨房禁烟的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  厨房就忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真昼在厨房帮忙是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实…实在是太抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕了一圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人差不多走光了  让你白跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  八千代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起  都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波在厨房帮忙了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是觉得不好意思的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把讨厌男人的缺点改了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  不要介意  佐藤他并没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是觉得出来接客有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟游要是来了的话  人手应该就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羞鸟游  你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妹妹的病情基本上好转了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.45,0:20:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想有什么可以帮忙的  就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我们啦  大家都很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹的病好了  真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不单是给店长的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:20:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给大家的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给伊波小姐添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说为什么你穿着厨房制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  之前真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话说的太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我才要和你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直  一直…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐也请品尝下慰问品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被店长全部吃掉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤和相马真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.74,0:21:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  毕竟是妹妹生病了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.81,0:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  为什么你们穿着大厅的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…说来话长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  佐藤心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:22:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤真温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能责怪女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没法责怪小鸟游
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.97,0:22:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  他这么讨厌接待客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い通りにゃすすまない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:16.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有点不能称心如意地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋に大事なコミュニケート
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达恋爱中最重要的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんなコトバが命中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样的言语才能打动她的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:25.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国語辞典をめくろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:25.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻翻国语辞典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:40.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おもむろに問わず語りで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.86,0:22:40.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再暧昧不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い気持ちを告げましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢地把炽热的心意告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,されどインギンなこの胸は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:46.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心中的这份真情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:49.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ジョウゼツにはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:49.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法口若悬河的表达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物音にデリケートです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.86,0:22:52.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点胆小敏感的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:55.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守る身の術しりません
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.90,0:22:55.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会防身术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど担当は矢面です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:22:58.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作护花使者是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:01.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常に現場勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:01.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意気を高らかに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:04.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中满怀着激情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.91,0:23:09.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自弁モードにTRYしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.91,0:23:09.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按自己的风格行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:13.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートのエッジに挑もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:13.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起挑战心灵的极限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:16.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うだけ見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:16.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想尽情与你对视
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:19.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もしかしたらとアトランダム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:19.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许时机难以预测
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,チャンスを待ってみるべき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:22.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也会耐心等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートのエースを捲ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:25.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出自己心中的王牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念力で見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾注心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の形のシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼剪出爱的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イメージを探りだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照心中的理想形象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:37.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙い通りにすすみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:37.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想达成预期目标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:41.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ネコの背中をまねしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:41.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得蓄势待发随时准备出击

Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集轮到姐姐们出场了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宗  我不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在截稿前  浑身脏兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.17,0:23:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间也好脏乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  总比梢姐要好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“宗太的忧郁、小鸟游家的女人们”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会加油的
